messages.content: [M/N] hey shale
[M/N] polaris wants to go shopping with you and your girlfriends can we make that happen
[B.B] Wow. Sure, I'll message the gang
[M/N] hey
[M/N] i have a question its really important
[B.B] Yeah what's up?
[M/N] polaris thinks ive got no self control or something but I think hes just hot and i am a victim of the situation
[M/N] what is your opinion
[Butterfly Bro is typing....]
[B.B] U h
[B.B] listen I'd say I'd need context normally but uh
[B.B] I guess it's a mixture of both...? You're certainly not as restrained as the average mun so I'll. Leave it at that
[M/N] thats useless but thank you
[B.B] ...you're welcome
[B.B]  we need to talk
[B.B] asap.
[M/N] shale im sick and fucking tired of waiting
[B.B] Do you want to attack? Because I agree
[M/N] i have plans drawn up we need to make our move
[B.B] On it. I'll be right over
[M/N] shale
[M/N] shale this is urgent are there any plasma on our side occupying any of nexums safehouses
[B.B] I don't think so??? Do you need me there?
[M/N] as long as you dont try to fuck anything up
[M/N] i have intel on polaris he isn't in the plasma zone right now
[B.B] oh my god. I'll be right there, this could be our chance-
[B.B] hey, mind if you could come over for a while? Or I could come over to your place whatever works
[M/N] busy
[M/N] why
[B.B] planning some stuff. It's to do with Polaris. We're both in agreement that you'd be helpful here
[M/N] so hell talk to you then
[M/N] i talk to him and he tells me hes gone forever, but hell make plans with you? this better not be some bullshit
[B.B] it's not like that, he just came to me first. I don't know why and I'm in agreement that he should have talked to you first
[M/N] he did talk to me he just told me that he wasnt coming back
[M/N] whatever. ill head over
[M/N] fuck
[B.B] I'm sorry.
[B.B] er- I'm at my place, so
[M/N] yeah

[B.B] Small report. Venor, Lamia, and Quartz have, I assume, completed their mission to take out the tesseract room. We have two new muns from the Plasma Zone, though. I'll take them in for questioning
[M/N] who are they
[B.B] polaris' mother
[B.B] and solum
[B.B] I am possibly in shock
[M/N] holy shit
[M/N] where is she im coming over
[B.B] My house. I have her secure. If she makes any wrong moves i'm cutting off her hand/s
[M/N] got it
[B.B] shit, Morise kidnapped my sister and Venor's maybe dead, probably a prisoner-
[B.B] please. Can you give me some good news
[B.B] do we have safehouses. if so where are they
[B.B] I uh offered protection in exchange for info from Solum
[M/N] no idea
[M/N] nobody tells me anything i dont know if we have that shit
[B.B] hm. I'll just uhhh take him to a random place then? Maybe Venor's old hut or smthng
[M/N] sure
[M/N] sorry for being awol i feel like shit. tell me if you need me
[B.B] will do. Have you been talking to Polaris?
[M/N] yeah
[M/N] weve been communicating through mindscape
[M/N] venor is with him they have escape plan
[B.B] oh sweet. tell me if there's any events or if I need to cause distractions or some shit
[M/N] if i get more info ill let you know
[M/N] apparently morise is fused with polaris have you heard any news on it
[M/N] pol says theyre attacking civilians, not sure if still active
[M/N] im going to get out and find out what i can, just wanted to communicate what I know
[B.B] oh jeez, I'll head out to the town square, see if I can find anyone injured
[M/N] alright
[M/N] meet you there asap
[B.B] sure
